cells.data: -- enumFromThenToChar :: Char -> Char -> Char -> [Char]on enumFromThenToChar(x1, x2, y)	set {int1, int2, intY} to {id of x1, id of x2, id of y}	set xs to {}	repeat with i from int1 to intY by (int2 - int1)		set end of xs to character id i	end repeat	return xsend enumFromThenToChar
